## 6. Validation Strategy Details

### 6.1 Validation Flow

```
Request
   |
   v
+------------------+
| express-validator |  <- Sanitize inputs (trim, escape)
| chain execution   |  <- Validate constraints
+------------------+
   |
   v
+------------------+
| validate.middleware |  <- Check validation results
+------------------+
   |
   +-- Invalid --> Throw ValidationError --> errorHandler --> 400 Response
   |
   +-- Valid --> Continue to Controller
```

### 6.2 Sanitization Rules

| Field | Sanitization | Purpose |
|-------|--------------|---------|
| title | trim(), escape() | Remove whitespace, prevent XSS |
| description | trim(), escape() | Remove whitespace, prevent XSS |
| status | trim(), toLowerCase() | Normalize input |
| id (param) | trim() | Clean UUID input |

