## 7. Error Handling Strategy

### 7.1 Error Hierarchy

```
AppError (abstract)
    |
    +-- ValidationError (400)
    |      - Field-level errors object
    |
    +-- NotFoundError (404)
    |      - Resource name parameter
    |
    +-- UnauthorizedError (401) [Phase 2]
    |
    +-- ForbiddenError (403) [Phase 2]
    |
    +-- ConflictError (409)
    |
    +-- TooManyRequestsError (429)
    |      - retryAfter parameter
    |
    +-- InternalServerError (500)
```

### 7.2 Prisma Error Mapping

| Prisma Code | HTTP Status | Application Error |
|-------------|-------------|-------------------|
| P2002 | 400 | ValidationError (unique constraint) |
| P2025 | 404 | NotFoundError |
| P2003 | 400 | ValidationError (foreign key) |
| P2014 | 400 | ValidationError (required relation) |
| Other | 500 | InternalServerError |

### 7.3 Error Response Examples

**Validation Error:**
